claim: Flublok (quadrivalent) was evaluated in the pivotal trial against Fluarix (quadrivalent standard-dose vaccine).
explanation: A CONSORT-style flow diagram showing 4,648 subjects enrolled and randomized to receive either FluBlok (n=2,344) or placebo (n=2,304), with details on discontinuations and resulting safety populations. does not support the claim because the pivotal trial comparator shown is placebo, not Fluarix (quadrivalent standard-dose vaccine). Note: No mention of Fluarix in the diagram; only placebo is used as the comparator.
